listing.description: Welcome home! This updated 2 bed, 2 bath, 2 entry, 2 level oasis with deeded parking spot is 5 min from Assembly Row, Rt 93, and Wellington Orange Line. Very own laundry (w&d) in basement. Central AC budgeted for Spring '21. This penthouse of a 3-unit assoc. is immersed in natural light with skylights/cathedral ceilings and features hardwood floors, granite countertops, and ample storage. Both beds boast full baths, blackout shades & own entrances. Lower-level studio suite has 3 walls of windows, water hook-up & extra area for seating/office. Top floor master bed has double-deep walk-in closet. Open-concept kitchen/living area & 2nd bath (with jaw-dropping shower AND clawfoot tub) complete the upper floor. NEW: fence '16, roof '17, water heater '18. Express Bus & Target/Starbucks \x3c2 blocks. Professionally landscaped yard, great outdoor space, & paved drive (resealed Sep '20) in lovely neighborhood. Open Houses Sat 12/5 12-2p, Sun 12/6 11a-1p. Lockbox also avail (call/text to setup).
